            <thetext>Up and down keys move the selection left and right whilst the left and right keys do nothing.

Petr has offered to have a look at this

Initial thoughts:
on key press
   if key = right
     childIndex += horizontal ? 1 : numChildrenInCol
   else if key = left
     childIndex -= horizontal ? 1 : numChildrenInCol
   else if key = up
     childIndex -= horizontal ? numChildrenInRow : 1
   else if key = down
     childIndex += horizontal ? numChildrenInRow : 1</thetext>
